Title : List of international schools in Thailand
Text : There are 166 [[international school]]s in [[Thailand]] as of June 2016, according to the [[Office of the Private Education Commission]] (OPEC), which regulates the operation of all private schools in the country.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&pid=sites&srcid=b3BlYy5nby50aHxvcGVjfGd4OmVmMjAyN2M4NWM1Yjk1Yw |title=นานาชาติ 080659.xlsx |publisher=Office of the Private Education Commission |date=8 June 2016|accessdate=2 April 2017}}</ref> This is a comprehensive list, sorted by province, then alphabetically.

